      "text": "（琴乃の磨き上げた歌とダンスも引けを取っていない）\n（サニピと月ストは今も競い合い、高め合っているんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Her singing and dancing‚ honed by Kotono‚ is impressive too.）\n（Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest are still competing and elevating each other.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.439638703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
