      "text": "（今、私は琴乃ちゃんと一緒に）\n（麻奈さんの曲を歌ってるんだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Right now‚ I'm singing Mana-san's song）\n（with Kotono-chan…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.2666014033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
