      "text": "（練習の時のプレッシャーが嘘みたいに体が軽い）\n（歌っていて自然に笑顔が溢れてくる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The pressure from rehearsals feels like a distant memory.）\n（I can't help but smile naturally as I sing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.4999479609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_03-skr025.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈さん、観てくれていますか？）\n（私がこの舞台に立てたのは麻奈さんのおかげです）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana-san‚ are you watching?）\n（I owe this stage to you‚ Mana-san.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.5332792597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
