      "text": "（麻奈さんは私の恩人で、憧れで……）\n（言葉では言い表せないくらい特別な存在です）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana-san is my benefactor‚ my idol‚ and more…）\n（You're an indescribably special presence to me.）",
        "id": ""
