      "text": "（そんな大好きな麻奈さんの曲をライバルの）\n（琴乃ちゃんと一緒に歌えるなんて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（To sing the beloved song of Mana-san‚）\n（a person I admire so much‚ with Kotono-chan…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.6999571161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
