      "text": "（麻奈はよく言っていたな。いつか後輩が出来たら）\n（この曲を一緒に歌いたいって……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana used to say this a lot. Someday‚ when she had juniors…）\n（…she wanted to sing this song together.）",
        "id": ""
